                                <p>Our policy is to only collect the minimum amount of personal information necessary to fulfill your request or inquiry or for other legitimate purposes for which we process your data. If you believe that our websites have gathered excessive information about you, please contact us through the request/inquiry form to voice your concerns. We take such concerns seriously and will address them as promptly as possible.</p>
                                <p>We want to assure you that we do not have any intention of collecting sensitive information through our websites, except when it is required by law. Examples of sensitive information that we are referring to include race or ethnicity, political opinions, religious or philosophical beliefs, trade union membership, physical or mental health, genetic data, biometric data, sexual life or sexual orientation, and criminal records. We kindly request that you do not provide such sensitive information when using our websites.</p>
                                <p>When you provide us with your personal information by submitting a request or inquiry on our website, we will only use it with your consent. However, if you voluntarily share your business contact details with us, we may send you marketing communications or information in order to maintain a business relationship with you or the company you work for, and this is done on the basis of our legitimate interests. In some cases, we may also seek your explicit and informed consent before sending you such communications. We use cookies on our website with your consent and/or for our legitimate interests as described below.</p>
