                            <div class="content-section" id="four">
                                <h3 class="h5 mb-4 fw-bold">Cookies</h3>
                                <p>Cookies are tiny text files that can be placed and stored on your computer or other devices when you visit our websites. These files allow our websites to remember certain information about your browsing activity and preferences, such as login credentials or language settings, making it easier for you to navigate our site and access its features. Cookies can be set by our website or by third-party services that we use, such as Google Analytics. By using cookies, we can provide a more personalized and efficient user experience for you.</p>
                                <p>We use cookies to collect your browsing information and preferences, with your consent. Our websites remember your system and preferences for a better browsing experience. Essential cookies are necessary for website functionality. We do not share cookie information with third parties for marketing. You can disable cookies in your web browser settings.</p>
                                <p>To better understand how visitors interact with our websites and improve their experience, we use Google Analytics to collect and analyze data about website traffic. Google Analytics uses cookies to track users' behavior and interactions with our websites. This allows us to gain insight into how visitors use our websites and identify areas for improvement. By using this information, we can make necessary changes to enhance the user experience. Rest assured that any information collected through Google Analytics is used only for analytical purposes and is not shared with third parties for marketing purposes.</p>
                                <p>We may use cookies to record your consent on our websites, such as your agreement to the use of cookies. This ensures that we have a record of your preferences and that you don't have to repeatedly give your consent every time you visit our website. Rest assured that any consent information collected through cookies is used solely for the purposes stated in our privacy policy and is not shared with third parties for marketing purposes.</p>
                                <p>We use cookies to ensure the technical functionality of our websites, based on our legitimate interest in providing a high-quality user experience. When we use cookies to remember your choices or for analytical purposes, we do so with your explicit consent. This means that we only collect and use cookie data for purposes that you have agreed to, and we will not share this information with third parties for marketing purposes. By obtaining your consent, we ensure that you have control over the use of cookies on our websites, and that your privacy and personal data are protected.</p>
                                <p>If you wish to opt-out of analytics tracking, you can disable cookies by adjusting your browser settings or by visiting the Google Analytics Opt-out Browser Add-on page at https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout/. By opting out, you can prevent Google Analytics from collecting and processing data about your website visits. Rest assured that you can still browse our websites even if you choose to opt-out of analytics tracking. However, please note that disabling cookies may affect your overall browsing experience and some features of our websites may not function as intended.</p>
                                <p>To disable other cookies, please visit www.allaboutcookies.org for more information. However, please note that disabling cookies may result in our websites or some of their parts becoming inaccessible or not functioning properly. Additionally, you may not be able to use some of the interactive features of our websites if you disable cookies.</p>
                            </div>

                            <div class="content-section" id="five">
                                <h3 class="h5 mb-4 fw-bold">Who may access your personal data</h3>
                                <p>We may share your personal data with our employees who are responsible for communicating with you or managing our marketing efforts. Additionally, we may disclose your data to our affiliated companies, some of which may be located outside of the European Union, as well as third-party service providers. Rest assured that we only share your information with trusted parties who have a legitimate need to access it for the purposes stated in our privacy policy.</p>
                                <p>We may grant access to statistical data about our website visitors to our employees in the marketing and IT departments who are responsible for analyzing and improving our websites. Additionally, our affiliated companies (some of which may be located outside of the European Union) and third-party service providers may also have access to this information. Please note that we only share statistical data and ensure that access is only granted to trusted parties with a legitimate need for the information.</p>
