                            <div class="content-section" id="six">
                                <h3 class="h5 mb-4 fw-bold">Transfers to third countries</h3>
                                <p>As a multinational group of companies, we may transfer and store your personal data in countries outside of the one where you are located. This could include countries outside of the European Economic Area that do not have an adequate level of personal data protection.</p>
                                <p>Since some of our offices are located in countries that do not meet the EU's standard of personal data protection, we use Standard Contractual Clauses approved by the EU to transfer personal data to these offices. These clauses meet the EU's requirements for transferring personal data to data processors/controllers located outside the EU. You can request copies of these clauses by contacting our data protection officer.</p>
